data.description: Check out this 4 bedroom and 3 full bathroom home located in Forest Glen at Bayside Lakes. New Roof just installed.  This split floor plan has vaulted ceilings and is very open and bright.  The kitchen has new granite countertops with 42'' maple cabinets, stainless steel appliances, built-in computer desk, and breakfast bar.  Large master bedroom with his and her walk-in closets, soaking tub, and dual sinks. Great backyard with vinyl fencing, Brick paver driveway and hurricane shutters for extra peace of mind.  Panel is wired for a generator if you wish to install one. Schedule your appointment today.
